## Tareas citas recibidas

%pyspark
rdd = sc.textFile("../datos/cite75_99.txt")
print(rdd.take(2))

%pyspark
rddT = rdd.filter(lambda l: '"CITING","CITED"' not in l).map(lambda l: l.split(","))
print(rddT.take(2))

%pyspark
from operator import add
claveValor = rddT.map(lambda (c,v): (v,1))
print(claveValor.take(2))
ncitas = claveValor.reduceByKey(add).cache()
print(ncitas.take(2))
print(ncitas.lookup('3986997'))

%pyspark
ncitasSortedByValues = ncitas.map(lambda (c, v) : (v,c)).sortByKey(ascending=False)
print(ncitasSortedByValues.take(10))

%pyspark
import numpy as np
nrdd = sc.parallelize(np.random.normal(size= 10000)).cache()
sts = nrdd.stats()
print("Resumen estadístico: \n{}".format(sts))

%pyspark
from math import fabs
stddev = sts.stdev()
avg = sts.mean()
frdd = nrdd.filter(lambda x: fabs(x- avg) < 3* stddev).cache()
print("Cantidad outliers: {}".format(sts.count() - frdd.count()))
